LEVI DAO 签署关于各国探测及使用外空包括月球与其他天体之活动所应遵守原则之条约

LEVI DAO signed a treaty on the principles that countries should observe in the exploration and use of outer space, including the moon and other celestial bodies.

https://www.un.org/zh/documents/treaty/files/A-RES-2222(XXI).shtml
